%p The film starts with classic architectural designs. Panning across shapes, exploring light. It gradually takes on harder subjects, shooting the buildings within their environment. The detail is so well realised that it takes the fantastical to remind us we're watching a representation rather than the actuality.

%p And indeed, as the piece goes on, it introduces tiny elements of the surreal.

