%h2 Resolution

%p I'm not one for New Year This and New Year That, and I realise I often use these articles to talk about how I'm reinventing my motivation and life - again. But nonetheless: this year I'll be pushing myself to do more in the personal stakes. To deliver such quality production of sites that I can be as proud of them as I am of what I'm paid to do.

%p Seems a tall order, so I'll have to break it down. The two obvious contenders for are Slidestream and Lachstock. Luckily, I already started with the latter on holidays. New stuff coming soon!

